    "These web-based gadgets provide unfathomable amounts of data that may be used to understand customer behaviors, styles, unique information, etc.",
    "They cannot be ignored.",
    "Many projects don't know how to store and cycle such enormous amounts of data, though.",
    "This is impeding the IoT's ability to grow and expand.",
    "In this case, the ability of man-made intelligence to sort through the avalanche of data produced by IoT devices may be of great use."
